    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >几个世纪后，地形改造（Terraforming）技术得以发展，人类开拓了多个星球，并在无数行星上生活。你是一名穿梭于各个星球的佣兵兼旅行者，却意外迫降在一颗被纳米机器占领的星球上。为了弄清这颗星球究竟发生了什么，请展开探索并收集资源。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索多种区域</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索这颗星球上的各个不同区域。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097220/extras/401180dffd51600e5121b64b91d462fb.poster.avif?t=1771849844\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097220/extras/401180dffd51600e5121b64b91d462fb.webm?t=1771849844\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097220/extras/401180dffd51600e5121b64b91d462fb.mp4?t=1771849844\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多样的怪物</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这颗星球上存在各种各样的威胁。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1 感染体</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被纳米机器感染的生命体，会为了感染你而冲过来的单纯生物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097220/extras/6c7ecb5c43d4f4bd050c1f2b482be812.poster.avif?t=1771849844\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097220/extras/6c7ecb5c43d4f4bd050c1f2b482be812.webm?t=1771849844\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097220/extras/6c7ecb5c43d4f4bd050c1f2b482be812.mp4?t=1771849844\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2 机器人</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >原本是协助人类工作的劳动者，但在被纳米机器侵蚀后开始攻击人类。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097220/extras/8a2d215734b66252c0c02e20be695d41.poster.avif?t=1771849844\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097220/extras/8a2d215734b66252c0c02e20be695d41.webm?t=1771849844\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097220/extras/8a2d215734b66252c0c02e20be695d41.mp4?t=1771849844\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >3 纳米变形体 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由纳米机器聚合形成的新生命体，会展现分裂、伪装等多种独特行为模式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097220/extras/e40d487d18ab5f1f70767ca1dc8a49d7.poster.avif?t=1771849844\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097220/extras/e40d487d18ab5f1f70767ca1dc8a49d7.webm?t=1771849844\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097220/extras/e40d487d18ab5f1f70767ca1dc8a49d7.mp4?t=1771849844\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >资源与采矿</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过击败敌人，或分解矿物与各种残骸来获取资源。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097220/extras/d8a4790f3659870fa74c19f329e94e29.poster.avif?t=1771849844\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097220/extras/d8a4790f3659870fa74c19f329e94e29.webm?t=1771849844\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097220/extras/d8a4790f3659870fa74c19f329e94e29.mp4?t=1771849844\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >用获得的资源制作多种装备</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >制作各种装备，并使用它们击败敌人或进行探索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097220/extras/b4f0a88d90aec0ad62d1d4563f3c9b28.poster.avif?t=1771849844\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097220/extras/b4f0a88d90aec0ad62d1d4563f3c9b28.webm?t=1771849844\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097220/extras/b4f0a88d90aec0ad62d1d4563f3c9b28.mp4?t=1771849844\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>改造枪械与装备，打造只属于你的专属装备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097220/extras/6fe7860d9015b719ccd29384fc79c43e.poster.avif?t=1771849844\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097220/extras/6fe7860d9015b719ccd29384fc79c43e.webm?t=1771849844\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097220/extras/6fe7860d9015b719ccd29384fc79c43e.mp4?t=1771849844\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建造基地</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造基地来储存资源，制作装备或载具，并打造休息的地方。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097220/extras/5e4e459465be95f2b9ac4442ebbdb505.poster.avif?t=1771849844\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097220/extras/5e4e459465be95f2b9ac4442ebbdb505.webm?t=1771849844\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097220/extras/5e4e459465be95f2b9ac4442ebbdb505.mp4?t=1771849844\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
